{"tid":1531603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有朋友失蹤","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:52:46.000Z","uid":250415,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7004a98ed9f71b44d577d179297524b4e40a7d","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"我WhatsApp 見佢last seen 係琴晚20:00<br />\n打電話又去左留言 又唔知佢去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以去邊到求助"},{"pid":"aefc1713aefebddb6024ef66e8c61a30b4b5eaa4","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:58.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"4c3133da3247b42835c0b9daba321a1b51fbeacd","tid":1531603,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"26915119bbbb503ab811ea0f4ea10da2b05940b4","tid":1531603,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e638709e7866db30260e3cf96296a459e3f8ef","tid":1531603,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"打去星火問有冇依個姓名嘅人係警署<br />\n最好知道埋佢之前係邊度示威"},{"pid":"d78f8d09b73e883d0a8fe93a4dbe4f24e5bcc648","tid":1531603,"uid":245658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0070af03afb21c0ce697562e0eab5c36e399b327","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:28:44.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"4a11045f61f0b81b39f8efa5b4f825cec7b674d0","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"5d122bb63ad0951e9e70c7d4bcdfa008e1cecae5","tid":1531603,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"你搵左佢屋企人先啦"},{"pid":"8dc9cf340135c251f02dc80cd5f3aec6db3f8521","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"93128ee90cc28f22b421efeeca6132629ef52fb7","tid":1531603,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e638709e7866db30260e3cf96296a459e3f8ef","tid":1531603,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"打去星火問有冇依個姓名嘅人係警署<br />\n最好知道埋佢之前係邊度示威"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8a797c5e238bd62bc728bdc8437341adeb90d3f","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d122bb63ad0951e9e70c7d4bcdfa008e1cecae5","tid":1531603,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"你搵左佢屋企人先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"就係無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得佢contact"},{"pid":"22923b595d5be243733e8ede9195a3a3e714e973","tid":1531603,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8a797c5e238bd62bc728bdc8437341adeb90d3f","tid":1531603,"uid":250